song_lyrics: Dīp utsavī āī, anupam dīp utsavī āī... Ṭek
Chau dish dīpmāḷ ati sohat, shobhā baranī na jāī;
Dīpmāḷ madhya sinhāsan par, rājat Shrīhari rāī;
Durgapur vāsi ati prem-magan hoy, gāvat gun Prabhutāī;
Muktānandke Nāthku nirakhat, dino he jag visarāī;
title: Dīp utsavī āī anupam
